text: yahood to kahate hain ki azeez khuda ke bete hain aur eesaee kahate hain ki maseeha (eesa) khuda ke bete hain ye to unakee baat hai aur (vah khud) unheen ke munh se ye log bhee unheen kaafiron kee see baaten banaane lage jo unase pahale guzar chuke hain khuda unako qatl (tahas nahas) karake (dekho to) kahaan se kahaan bhatake ja rahe hain
